</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\">
<img src=\"https://sailboatdata.com/storage/EQ67ePlpXnphm3ao52D8BFPPyLqJ1rm8ShsnzY7A.jpeg\" alt=\"\"/>
<figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A generic photo of the Sun Odyssey 42.2 from original sales materials.</figcaption>
</figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Akaton is 12.3 meters long, and 4.1 meters wide with a 2 meter draft. She has 3 cabins (she has a 4 cabin layout, with the seperators removed to convert the bunks into shelves).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\">
